<item>
            <title>[LU-11272] LNet Health: handle routing special case</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11272</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are two issues:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A router checker ping can timeout, causing the mdh to be invalidated. We need to recreate the mdh in that case&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;When re-transmitting a message, even if the peer is marked as down we should re-transmit the message to fulfill it&apos;s retry quota.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
